Pablo Andrés Rivero
[writes](http://www.pabloarivero.com/2011/06/fotografiando-el-gran-poder.html)
[es] about the ‘[Gran
Poder](http://www.boliviahostels.com/travelguide/festivals.html#poder)‘
festival in La Paz. Pablo describes the music, dances and colorful clothing
worn during the parades. He also links to his set of photos of the event [on
Flickr](http://www.flickr.com/photos/parivero/sets/72157626874044155/) under a
Creative Commons license.

